  "title": "F&B Management Trainee (Service)",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1><p><strong>Baker & Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery & foodstore is hiring!</p><h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3><p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p><p>✅ 6-days work week</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🍕 Outlets: Asian Civilizations Museum </strong>| <strong>Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Guoco Midtown) | Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Jewel) | Chip Bee Garden | Dairy Farm | Dempsey | Eng Kong Park | Hillcrest | Namly Place | South Bouna Vista | Serangoon Garden | Swan Lake | Sunset Way</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p><ul><li>Hands-on involvement in daily operation to understand and execute duties</li><li>Undertake management trainings and responsibilities with focus on sales management, customer satisfaction, operating expenses and shop’s profitability</li><li>Focus mainly on Service/ FOH, but will have exposure to Kitchen/ BOH. May cover Kitchen/ BOH if operationally required</li><li>Enforce and ensure compliance to Company SOPs, governmental regulations, food safety and hygiene standards within the store</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational needs</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Passionate about service and people</li><li>Preferably Diploma in Hospitality or related fields</li><li>Good team player and self-motivated</li><li>6-days work week and able to work on weekends/public holidays</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Medical + Dental benefits</li><li>Birthday vouchers</li><li>Staff discounts across brands</li><li>Sales incentives</li><li>6 day work week</li><li>Company insurance</li><li>Free Staff Meals</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7</p><p>** T&C applies<br /></p>",
